<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; color: #333; }
        .btn { 
            background-color: #000; color: #fff; 
            padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Hi {{customerName}},</p>
    
    <p>Please find attached your quotation <strong>{{quotationNumber}}</strong>.</p>
    
    {{#if link}}
    <p>You can also view and download it online here:</p>
    <p>
        <a href="{{link}}" class="btn">View Quotation</a>
    </p>
    {{/if}}

    <p>If you have any questions, just reply to this email.</p>
    
    <br>
    <p>Best regards,<br>The Sales Team</p>
</body>
</html>